[05:45] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'disadvantages. These are really nice PC radios. They work really well. They\'re so easy to use and set up. And the fact that the SIM card is included along with the data plan is just completely game-changing compared to other PC'

[05:57] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'devices out of China. The USB charging is handy. You don\'t need a specific charging base. There\'s no fiddly computer programming and cables to mess around with, and they obviously have a significant range advantage over'

