AUDIO: 'coverage is patchy. So, there\'s about half a second of latency. But again, that\'s not the radio\'s fault. One other point to note is that you can only use these with other PC1 handsets. And other than that, I\'m nitpicking. I really'

[07:02] [scene:talk]
